Enum StandardCommands

  • java.lang.Object

    public enum StandardCommands
extends java.lang.Enum<StandardCommands>
implements org.keyple.commands.CommandsTable
    Storage Card Functionality Support compliant with PCSC Specification Part 3 chapter 3.2.2.1

    PO and CSM commands enumeration. Each enumeration provides the type (PO/CSM), the name, the command builder and the response parser.
